{"tid":813033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英籍幼稚園老師下課變身毒販　天水圍出貨斷正","createTime":"2018-09-10T06:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T13:47:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2260aa95a039fb8edb69e037a26ddc30a6929e2b","tid":813033,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180910/photo/bkn-20180910090110121-0910_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180910134837\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180910%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180910090110121-0910_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180910134837&h=a28909f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗警區特別職務隊根據線報及經深入調查後，今日(10日)凌晨約2時展開打擊毒品行動，趁一名36歲英籍男子駕車抵達天水圍天恩路一酒店時上前截查，英漢情緒激動反抗，以手襲擊兩名警員，但終被制服。 <br />\n<br />\n警員在他身上檢獲約30克懷疑大麻及四枚含有懷疑「D-麥角酸二乙胺」（俗稱LSD）的毒郵票，行動中檢獲的毒品總值約9千港元。其後召來緝毒犬到場協助搜查私家車，但未有進一步發現，英漢涉嫌販毒及襲警被捕。一名38歲及一名27歲的警員分別腹部及膝部受傷，需要送屯門醫院治理。 <br />\n<br />\n據消息指，被捕英籍男子身材健碩，更曾學習過搏擊，遇查時發難打傷兩名警員，他報稱在幼稚園任教，警方正調查毒品來源。毒郵票又稱「迷幻郵票」，在外國較為普遍，在港則甚為罕見，一般在外國人較多的娛樂場所發現，而在新界北則首次檢獲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180910/bkn-20180910090110121-0910_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180910%2Fbkn-20180910090110121-0910_00822_001.html&d=aYDE9KzYsOpxgFxiHX9xqwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=18b51ece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180910/bkn-20180910090110121-0910_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b64766f1ea68f6e5092bc42e8712b610bbf6f004","tid":813033,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T06:37:39.000Z","msg":"黑警英文咁屎，點落口供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc29cf27d08425d990635f26aaad44c302c3b1f6","tid":813033,"uid":23180,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"Breaking Bad?"},{"pid":"45610c6742075f6c9b25ef70cab8fa2b7fd7d3a5","tid":813033,"uid":63950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T06:47:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8da8fcc45883c68182a9d1d8887166cce4be8583","tid":813033,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:25:39.000Z","msg":"Say my name"},{"pid":"3eadc7dc0005e298e40dc78e6c49a8c8660caec4","tid":813033,"uid":109690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.clublexus.com/forums/attachments/sc430-2nd-gen-2001-2010/162861d1264571837-3-76-supra-lsd-differential-diy-sc430-dsc05940.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clublexus.com%2Fforums%2Fattachments%2Fsc430-2nd-gen-2001-2010%2F162861d1264571837-3-76-supra-lsd-differential-diy-sc430-dsc05940.jpg&h=60684575&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d225b4d960391879b1cb01543a933188ada4387","tid":813033,"uid":78143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/214625_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F214625_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=e13fb73c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/214628_86d0fa7ddd0c478998039a210fbecfa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F214628_86d0fa7ddd0c478998039a210fbecfa6.jpg&h=c7fa3316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/214633_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F214633_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg&h=db634744&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}